Mondi Rises Most in Four Days in Johannesburg as First-Half Profit to Gain

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-22T07:06:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-22/mondi-rises-most-in-four-days-in-johannesburg-as-first-half-profit-to-gain.html
Mondi Ltd. (MND) ,  Europe ’s largest maker
of office paper, climbed the most in four days after saying so-
called underlying operating profit for the first half of the
fiscal year will be “considerably higher” than a year earlier.  The stock advanced 1.73 rand, or 3.2 percent, to 56.23 rand
by 9:04 a.m. in Johannesburg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  